dct_title_s: Belgian Congo, roads, railroads and navigable waterways
dct_description_sm: drawn in the Branch of Research and Analysis, OSS.
Shows road conditions, railroad gauges, and year-round and seasonally navigable rivers.
"This map includes only the main roads compiled from 1940 official road maps (1:1,000,000) and special reports in the Office of Strategic Service s."
